The '''Professiona Artists Guild''' was a group of noted artists that were gathered together in the [[Elrood sector/Legends|Elrood sector]]. The organization was based out of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Akana]], but they also maintained a presence in other areas of the [[Sector/Legends|sector]]. The guild had a permanent place in the [[Perma (buildings)|Perma]] within the [[Elrood Bazaar]] on the planet [[Elrood/Legends|Elrood]]. This location, the largest such marketplace in the entire sector allowed their artwork to be seen by a multitude of beings and increased their sales considerably. One of the famous paintings done by the guild was known as [[The Lovers' Dilemma]] which had been created by the artist known as [[Walls]]. The painting hung within the guild's residence in the Elrood Bazaar, where it was displayed proudly.

